parameters.name: updateImageSetMetadataUpdates
parameters.description: Update image set metadata updates. DICOMUpdates (dict) --- The object containing removableAttributes and updatableAttributes. removableAttributes (bytes) --- The DICOM tags to be removed from ImageSetMetadata. updatableAttributes (bytes) --- The DICOM tags that need to be updated in ImageSetMetadata. revertToVersionId (string) --- Specifies the previous image set version ID to revert the current image set back to.
